-Instalar o RabbitMQ:
 download Erlang/OTP:
  https://packages.erlang-solutions.com/erlang/#tabs-debian     
  instalar com sudo dpkg -i nome_do_pacote

 download RabbitMQ.deb:
 https://github.com/rabbitmq/rabbitmq-server/releases/download/v3.7.5/rabbitmq-server_3.7.5-1_all.deb
 instalar com sudo dpkg -i nome_do_pacote

 Instalar Pika
  pip install pika
  documentação pika: https://pika.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html

Start the RabbitMQ server:
sudo service rabbitmq-server start

-Instalar Tkinter
sudo apt-get install python-tk